            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nemesi <lb n="2"/>deae <expan><abbr>Ter</abbr><ex>entius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Marc<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>an<lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>s b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> tem<lb break="no" n="5"/>pl<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>m</abbr></expan> a novo <lb n="6"/>fecit ex <lb n="7"/>viso <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Altar oder Statuenbasis. Corona nicht erhalten. Inschriftfeld in zwei Teile gebrochen.</p>
            </div>
